.TH DESGRANA-GUI 1 "May 2026" "desgrana 1.6.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
desgrana-gui \- graphical interface for desgrana
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B desgrana-gui
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B desgrana-gui
is a graphical front-end for
.BR desgrana (1).
Drop a session directory onto the window to load it, adjust stereo pairs
if needed, choose an output directory, and click Split.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR desgrana (1)
.PP
Project homepage: https://github.com/rdalverny/desgrana
